1. build base images and push to internet

```
pushd docker-images
docker build -t 909427826938.dkr.ecr.eu-west-2.amazonaws.com/lotus-oni-base -f Dockerfile.lotus-oni-base .

aws ecr get-login-password \
    --region eu-west-2 \
| docker login \
    --username AWS \
    --password-stdin 909427826938.dkr.ecr.eu-west-2.amazonaws.com

docker push 909427826938.dkr.ecr.eu-west-2.amazonaws.com/lotus-oni-base:latest
```

